This paper is primarily focused on face recognition, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with image and video processing, which could place it under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper proposes a novel block for enhancing the performance of deep networks, which could also place it under neural networks (cs.NE).
